{"tid":1515794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵綠衫人做問卷 問服務質素！！！","createTime":"2019-08-29T10:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T10:44:30.000Z","uid":160147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"32759a6ce7ff1a9f2e78c46ae4409db10155d08f","tid":1515794,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"啱啱返屋企搭鐵<br />\n閘入面有綠衫人叫我做問卷<br />\n我答問題 <br />\n佢幫我剔<br />\n係服務質素評分<br />\n問準時，清潔，價錢，安全<br />\n我俾左1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後問左個人資料<br />\n1起點終點 <br />\n2本周搭車次數 <br />\n3年齡層 <br />\n4搭車目的<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知地鐵諗咩？依家評分咁低都做問卷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6a87d55f836380535f900f5d011abf68e78e1b","tid":1515794,"uid":34010,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"個人資料包括咩資料"},{"pid":"b9a6ff2269f94b5943e345fe95c75de96343ae23","tid":1515794,"uid":152976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:17:04.000Z","msg":"//4搭車目的//<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢期望可以有咩答案? 除咗代步之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3360e80178d760e079ee46e4c99d6b3ea0a855b5","tid":1515794,"uid":246586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"個人資料先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c2569716792c03d3978b7fefa268f5a7c5dda2","tid":1515794,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a6ff2269f94b5943e345fe95c75de96343ae23","tid":1515794,"uid":152976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:17:04.000Z","msg":"//4搭車目的//<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢期望可以有咩答案? 除咗代步之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"講得唔清楚<br />\n問你返工定返學定出街玩"},{"pid":"fa54a3f70616dec02ef